                            <comment id="240796" author="bzzz" created="Mon, 28 Jan 2019 13:27:34 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I&apos;m hitting this locally (very rare).. it seems the root cause is that failed mkdir can&apos;t cleanup the name sometimes, then subsequent lookup/stat/whatever finds that in broken state (the name and one stripe exist, but another stripe doesn&apos;t).&lt;/p&gt;
